---
// About Section Component
// Professional summary and highlights
---

<section id="about" class="about-section" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 id="about-heading" data-i18n="about.heading">
      Professional Summary
    </h2>
    <div class="about-content">
      <p class="lead" data-i18n="about.lead">
        Dynamic and highly creative software engineer with over 15 years
        of international experience delivering innovative solutions for
        leading companies in the US. Recognized for technical leadership,
        building and empowering high-performance teams, and driving
        continuous improvement.
      </p>
      <p data-i18n="about.content">
        Passionate about contributing as an
        <strong>individual contributor</strong> who bridges creativity,
        technical depth, and collaboration to deliver meaningful results.
        After a period dedicated to consulting and product R&D, I am eager
        to bring my expertise in
        <strong
          >innovation, automation, and digital transformation</strong
        >
        to forward-thinking organizations.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-highlights">
      <div class="highlight-item">
        <h3>
          <span
            aria-label="15 plus"
            data-i18n-aria-label="about.highlights.experience.aria_label"
            data-i18n="about.highlights.experience.value"
            >15+</span
          >
        </h3>
        <p data-i18n="about.highlights.experience.label">
          Years of Experience
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="highlight-item">
        <h3>
          <span
            aria-label="5 plus"
            data-i18n-aria-label="about.highlights.companies.aria_label"
            data-i18n="about.highlights.companies.value"
            >5</span
          >
        </h3>
        <p data-i18n="about.highlights.companies.label">
          Major Companies
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="highlight-item">
        <h3>
          <span
            aria-label="100 percent"
            data-i18n-aria-label="about.highlights.commitment.aria_label"
            data-i18n="about.highlights.commitment.value"
            >100%</span
          >
        </h3>
        <p data-i18n="about.highlights.commitment.label">
          Commitment to Quality
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
